---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
const prompt = `Create a 10-slide presentation outline for an internal business update.

Topic: AI tools rollout across KGM Australia
Audience: department managers and staff
Tone: practical, positive and not too corporate
Include:
1. Why we are introducing AI tools
2. What employees can use them for
3. Safety rules
4. ChatGPT vs Claude
5. Examples by department
6. Next steps

For each slide, provide title, key points and speaker notes.`;
---
<Layout title="Create Presentations | AI Hub"><section class="recipe"><div class="eyebrow">📈 Slides · 5 min</div><h1>Turn rough notes into a usable presentation.</h1><p class="lead">AI is useful for structure, story, speaker notes, slide titles and simplifying overloaded decks.</p><div class="panel"><h2>Prompt</h2><div class="prompt">{prompt}</div><button class="btn copy" data-copy={prompt}>Copy prompt</button></div></section></Layout>
